title: "AI Healthcare System: Open-Source Privacy-First Clinical AI, 3D DICOM PACS, & EHR Interoperability Platform"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-07-17"
repository-code: "https://github.com/pavanbadempet/AI-Healthcare-System"
url: "https://github.com/pavanbadempet/AI-Healthcare-System"
license: "MIT"
abstract: "A production-grade, privacy-first open-source Electronic Health Record (EHR) and Clinical Decision Support System (CDSS) built on React 19, FastAPI, and PySpark. Integrates 5 calibrated XGBoost diagnostic classifiers with SHAP explainability, stateful LangGraph multi-agent RAG supervisor with local Ollama inference, 3D Volumetric DICOM Multi-Planar Reconstruction (MPR) PACS rendering, ABDM ABHA Health ID consent lifecycle management, SMART on FHIR app sandboxing, and ANSI X12 837P insurance billing."
